@NODE History "History of Chat-O-Meter - Amazing... :)"
                  - -------------------------------------.
                 |  History: Something that once was...  |
                 `------------------------------------- -

   22-Jan-95   1.0.1    Fixed CoM-Convert; it now reads the name of the
                        user from the correct place.

   04-Jan-95   1.0.0    Completed CoM-Convert and restyled it.

   03-Jan-95   1.0.0    Created CoM-Convert.

   25-Dec-94   2.0.9    Chat-O-Meter can also run in silent mode now.
                        New tooltype: QUIET

   25-Dec-94   2.0.8    Merry X-Mas :) Made some internal changes, removed
                        the stack-check (smaller executable).

   24-Dec-94   2.0.7    Found the bug that caused the strange resets.
                        I adjusted the wrong variable... sigh... it
                        should be fixed now.

   24-Dec-94   2.0.6    Allocated memory for some structures by myself
                        instead of allocating them on the stack. Hope
                        to have fixed the strange guru's.

   24-Dec-94   2.0.5▀   Special version for Muad'Dib with DEBUG info.

   24-Dec-94   2.0.5    Tried to fix a bug that caused strange resets on
                        Muad'Dibs machine (040) and weird crashes on my
                        own system (total freeze and I had to turn my
                        computer off for at least one minute!).

   24-Dec-94   2.0.4    Fixed a bug that caused the bulletin only the be
                        updated in the event of a new entry in the Top
                        Ten. The Total Chat Time was never updated.
                        *Reported by Quartz*

   23-Dec-94   2.0.3    Built in the User file, now a record is kept of
                        every user. A new bulletin perhaps.
                        New tooltype: NO_USERFILE
                        
                        Altered the output after the chat again, now also
                        contains info about the user him/herself.

   22-Dec-94   2.0.2    Altered the output a bit and made some minor
                        internal changes that caused a smaller executable.

   21-Dec-94   2.0.1    Altered the output after a chat.

   21-Dec-94   2.0.0    Totally rewrote it from scratch:
                        - END_CHAT tooltype fixes the problem with lost
                          carriers and then starting a chat again causing
                          the start of the chat being the end of a chat.
                          (Never mind if you don't get it, it's fixed!)
                        *Requested by Quartz*

                        New layout from Stezothetic implemented.
                        *Thanks to Stezothetic*

   26-Oct-93   1.2      Output file is now sysop-configurable. Now you can
                        have it saved anywhere you like!
                        Released: 30-Oct-93

   23-Oct-93   1.1      Implemented safety-procedure so when user drops
                        carrier in chat the Chat-O-Top doesn't get mixed up.
                        Released at: 27-Oct-93

   17-Oct-93   1.0      First release to friends.
@ENDNODE

